27 27-413 For purposes of sections 27-414 and 27-415, offense of sexual
28 assault means:
29 (1) Any violation of section 28-316.01, section 5 of this act, or
30 sections 28-319 to 28-322.5;
31 (b) An sexual assault under section 28-319 or 28-320, sexual abuse
